com.bbn.tak.ml.mx_framework

Interface MXPlugin


  • public interface MXPlugin
    A model execution (MX) plugin.

    Supports the ability to create multiple instances of the same plugin, each with potentially different models and parameters.

    Implementing classes must use the MXPluginDescription annotation to describe the basic attributes of the plugin to the framework.

    Implementing classes must also use the appropriate instance of the MXFrameworkRegistrar to register and deregister the plugin.
